# Presenation of IV122 course work
[IV122 (czech ony)](http://www.fi.muni.cz/~xpelanek/IV122) is 2h/week seminar/class focused on solving various programming problems related to some mathematical concepts. 

### Navigation 
All my output for this course is in self explanatory [git repository](https://github.com/adekcz/IV122). This page only contains some notes to some problems.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
